{"tid":821214,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港原創既中世紀攻城策略boardgame 上線喔 [圖修正左]","createTime":"2018-09-16T00:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T00:50:21.000Z","uid":195137,"like":152,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5d3038cebeb68a469152f75228391c56ef6e53","tid":821214,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得一兩個月前我地出個post 問大家意見，之前條link 係度: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/747482/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/747482/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nUnrecorded Siege 係一幅中度策略遊戲，故事係講中世紀百年戰爭中間有一段未被記錄既攻城戰。唔止得一個玩法，我地造左好多唔同既戰役包括單人模式，一打一攻城，四人混戰同串連起唔同戰役概Legacy mode，各有各既故事同勝利條件。<br />\n上次俾大家睇左啲成品圖，而今次有好詳盡既圖去介紹我地既流程玩法(GIF修正左):<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">首先係選擇陣營</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/084040_aef68fa503f788855f502ca1e5351d74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F084040_aef68fa503f788855f502ca1e5351d74.jpg&h=47dd5989&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">法國同英國目有概兵種組合唔同，玩法都唔同。一邊用卡，一邊角色。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ctelroy.com/unrecorded_siege/unre_phase_GIF_v2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fctelroy.com%2Funrecorded_siege%2Funre_phase_GIF_v2.gif&h=d03825bc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n通常每回合主要都會有8個階段，根據唔同戰役會有小量分別。</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據陣形同玩法，睇下係回合入面完唔完成到目標，包括攻守城，收集資源，護送，佔特定地方等，核心流程大概就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得唔吸引，唔好插得太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，其實我地仲有幾日就會上Kickstarter，9月20號。 係之前我地想搞個giveaway， 抽中左既巴絲打梗係會有一盒Game啦，而且係Collection Pack， 會有角色模型。具體係每100個正評，就會係呢個post 度抽一個留左言既巴絲打。當kickstart 到100%，就會送番一副成品俾中獎既大家!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想試玩，可以上我地facebook約我地或者黎Join我地概試玩會，緊kickstarter期間會搞幾次。<br />\n<br />\nFB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnreSiege/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUnreSiege%2F&d=IvkgohKqJAFGbusf%2FYGjT%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=babf26b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UnreSiege/</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/unresiege/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Funresiege%2F&d=IvkgohKqJAFGbusf%2FYGjT%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=671fc840\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/unresiege/</a>"},{"pid":"27d71217818dbb025e71a92e3885c270dfa70a19","tid":821214,"uid":195137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"呢到GIF圖修正左，舊POST概正評同回覆都會計埋入giveaway到，<br />\n各位巴絲打放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"92347a19d9894fc2b26bce73c8724431d53ce58c","tid":821214,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"本土製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲commander會有miniature? (雖然睇ig圖好似唔mini<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"c1fc6f1fcdc9e3753dcaeb13cf5e9a174e380e79","tid":821214,"uid":655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:00:38.000Z","msg":"lm 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229b870fcf6fa526a3ef2fe4584dd4193e4af439","tid":821214,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92347a19d9894fc2b26bce73c8724431d53ce58c","tid":821214,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"本土製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲commander會有miniature? (雖然睇ig圖好似唔mini<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"會！貞德一定有<br />\n其他角色就要解鎖，解鎖晒有10隻以上<br />\n到時求支持，本土建模同製作，睇貞德就知，我自已真係覺得好細緻好靚<br />\n所以真心係想解鎖晒佢，整晒出黎俾大家。"},{"pid":"37a9d336a1b7463655252ccf99307d084fc829d7","tid":821214,"uid":199120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"冇細心睇咩黎，但見係本土game，當然要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f483e8019791a89d0032427a56d254afa649db26","tid":821214,"uid":137764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"1170581452ca622c794f2efe7712ee4d7d51b03a","tid":821214,"uid":165886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:09:14.000Z","msg":"Lm 支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b20d7571f393f2b5e9155c7d1bd7bf375deec0","tid":821214,"uid":133886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:10:14.000Z","msg":"lm支持"},{"pid":"30e95f92b6deb56e65604b2698f982fa67a2f31a","tid":821214,"uid":2561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acbc026c858e29be176ef1da78a17b9f5142c74","tid":821214,"uid":130190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"f7a059afd9a1b6f51410c31760aa58173404b4c4","tid":821214,"uid":157669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:22:19.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a5f466d0eda7cb09489029f5473c88209a054d","tid":821214,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:22:46.000Z","msg":"支持，好有心"},